However, Arsenal's immediate need for a striker is more pressing.

Given the injury to Olivier Giroud and Arsenal will hope that being a compatriot, Arsene Wenger will be able to persuade Remy he will have more first-team football at Arsenal given that Chelsea's first choice striker will clearly be Diego Costa.

